## 5. Composition rule — fragment → moment

De[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] reconstruct mot[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] moment tu[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] fragments, rule composition (seal):

| MomentKind | Required fragments | Optional fragments |
|---|---|---|
| SCAR | ENVELOPE, EVIDENCE | CAUSATION_CHAIN (recurrence_of), REMEDY, META |
| KHAI_SANG | ENVELOPE, INSIGHT_CONTENT | RELATED_CANONICAL, CAUSATION_CHAIN (related_to), META |
| GIAC_NGO | ENVELOPE, INNER_RESONANCE, RELATED_CANONICAL | CAUSATION_CHAIN (xac_nhan_from), META |
| MOTION_TICH_CUC | ENVELOPE, BODY_RESPONSE, CAUSATION_CHAIN (triggered_by) | META |

**Validation rule (seal):**

- Required fragments tat[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] ca[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] phai[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] co[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] (persister reject moment neu[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] thieu[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME])
- Optional fragments co[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] the[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] 0 hoac[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] nhieu[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME]
- Multiple fragments cung[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] kind trong 1 moment duoc[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] phep[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] (vi[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] du[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] 2 REMEDY cho 2 vaccin khac[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] nhau) — discriminate beng[C2:RN_ANG_ENG] `fragment_id`
- `ENVELOPE.causation` phai[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] equal `parent_moment_causation` — integrity check
- `parent_moment_kind` cua[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] mau[C5:RN_OI_AU] fragment trong moment phai[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] identical — integrity check

