## 6. Serialization — on-disk layout

Fragment schema KHONG[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] dau[C3:RN_OI_AU] storage mapping da[C4:RN_KEEP_RIME] seal o[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] SPEC_MOMENTS_MODULE_v0.2 §3 `storagePathsFor`. Fragment la[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] **representation layer** khi read/write content cua[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] file target, KHONG[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] phai[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] routing layer.

On-disk JSON structure cho mot[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] moment:

```json
{
  "moment": {
    "kind": "SCAR",
    "causation": "SCAR-20260426-FRAMING-SELF-CORRECT-LOOP",
    "sirasign_moment": "abc123..."
  },
  "fragments": [
    { "fragment_kind": "ENVELOPE", "fragment_id": "frag-envelope-0", "ordinal": 0, ... },
    { "fragment_kind": "EVIDENCE", "fragment_id": "frag-evidence-1", "ordinal": 1, ... },
    { "fragment_kind": "REMEDY", "fragment_id": "frag-remedy-2", "ordinal": 2, ... }
  ]
}
```

**Rule binding (seal):**

- `fragments` array SORT by `ordinal` khi persist
- `sirasign_moment` = SHA-256 cua[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] canonical-sorted fragments array + moment.kind + moment.causation
- Partial load (1 fragment only) duoc[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] phep[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] — persister verify fragment sirasign doc[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] lap[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME], khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] cen[C2:RN_AN_EN] load full moment

