1. Fragment union pass TypeScript strict (exhaustiveness check)
2. Validator script reject moment thieu[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] required fragments
3. Validator script reject fragment vau[C1:RN_OI_AU] `parent_moment_kind` mismatch
4. Validator script verify `sirasign_fragment` per fragment
